<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Never watched the movie so I don't know if the movie refers to the monster Mbwun as Dr. Whittlesey the whole time or what (in the book that's only rev<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Never watched the movie so I don't know if the movie refers to the monster Mbwun as Dr. Whittlesey the whole time or what (in the book that's only revealed in the epilogue) but I'm going to assume you're asking how the monster died in the book? The Mbwun was killed with a shot to the eye by Pendergast. No lucky bullet or anything like that involved. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
