<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I honestly don&apos;t think reading the book will ruin the movie. Like most adaptations there are some glaring differences but the key points are the same.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I honestly don't think reading the book will ruin the movie. Like most adaptations there are some glaring differences but the key points are the same. I just finished reading the book and watching the movie in 2021 and have to say that I love them both<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
