  <span id="freeText8717909729918587940" style="display:none">Have you ever read a book that was so intense and absorbing in some areas you were reading so fast, and you thought, ''did I read all of that part ?'' This is one of those books.<br />I have to thank Matthew for his recommendation on this one.<br />This was an enjoyable thriller read for me. Since I had worked before in an Art Museum as security personal and then curator, I could place myself in that atmosphere.<br />It was a great thriller with different twists <br />I can't wait to read more from these authors<br />This is a perfect novel to read right before you go to sleep at night =)</span>
