            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/72137025-j-k-grice?shelf=mystery-thriller">mystery-thriller</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2142533688" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13227877607222280107">RELIC is the book that launched the brilliant Agent Pendergast series. As with all Preston/Child books, this one offers plenty of science, adventure, and mystery. The Pendergast series is a testament to genuine genius on the part of these two amazing authors.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


