<span id="freeTextContainer11838606739567655296">This was recommended to me by several visitors to my site, but I&apos;m sorry folks, I simply couldn&apos;t finish it. Cardboard, cliched characters and a monster on a rampage in a museum don&apos;t quite add up to a great read. I gave it a good effort, the quick readability of it got me halfway through it but I don&apos;t care how it ends or who lives or dies. I&apos;m moving on. </span>
