        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1661345041" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3269968138878686133">I&apos;ve never rode a rollercoaster <s>because am too chicken to ride one</s>. While reading this book, I said to myself, <i>&quot;Is this is how a rollercoaster ride would feel? The extent of thrill boderdering on... horror?&quot;</i><br/>What an adrenaline rush has been, this ride I mean read! :D<br/>Enough said. I am off to read the sequel(s).<br/><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText3269968138878686133" style="display:none">I've never rode a rollercoaster <s>because am too chicken to ride one</s>. While reading this book, I said to myself, <i>"Is this is how a rollercoaster ride would feel? The extent of thrill boderdering on... horror?"</i><br />What an adrenaline rush has been, this ride I mean read! :D<br />Enough said. I am off to read the sequel(s).<br /><br /></span>
